oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Plowing fields
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Black and white photograph of a man in overalls, plowing downhill with two dark horses in Sumner County, Tenn. Several tree stumps are visible. A structure [house] is in the background behind a row of trees. One horse has a blaze on face.
